            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p><span>Woven from swaths of rich brocade silk and embroidered with ancient Azlanti script in golden thread, this stole imparts a noble appearance to even the homeliest of individuals when draped over the shoulders. While wearing a stole of civility, you receive a +2 item bonus to Diplomacy checks to Make an Impression with humans or Make a Request of humans, and a +2 item bonus to Intimidation checks against humans. The stole also grants you full understanding of the Azlanti language.<br></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Activate</strong> <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">A</span> envision; <strong>Frequency</strong> once per day; <strong>Requirements</strong> you are a human; <strong>Effect</strong> You gain 10 temporary Hit Points, which last for 10 minutes.&nbsp;</span></p>"
